llance, or chains, into their kin and communal relationships.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0https://www.aup.nl/en/publish/open-access  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 4aEarly Modern Studies. 4aHealth and Medicine. 4aHistory, Art History, and Archaeology. 4aHistory. 4aPsychology. 4aSociology and Social History. 7aHISTORY / Europe / France.2bisacsh  aMadness, Insanity Defense, Pardon, Community.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311068955608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP ROW Ebook Package English 2020z978311069630140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048533329zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048533329zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048533329/original  a978-3-11-068955-6 Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-069629-5 DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  a978-3-11-069630-1 PP ROW Ebook Package English 2020b2020  a978-3-11-075400-1 EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-GOA